### Management Commands

**Create or update a local user:**
```bash
cd ~/cmdb_web
python3 manage.py createuser <username> --password <password> [--admin] [--email user@corp.pvt]
```

**List all users:**
```bash
python3 manage.py listusers
```

**Restart the web service:**
```bash
sudo systemctl restart cmdb-web
```

**View live service logs:**
```bash
sudo journalctl -u cmdb-web -f
```

**Run a manual full sync:**
```bash
~/vcenter/cmdb_cron.sh full
```

**Run a manual fast sync:**
```bash
~/vcenter/cmdb_cron.sh fast
```

**Run fast sync in dry-run mode (no DB writes):**
```bash
python3 ~/vcenter/cmdb_sync_fast.py --dry-run
```
